{"tid":2487931,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"兩學生被控警察宿舍外藏有腐蝕性液體 今裁定罪名不成立 女生曾一度還柙近兩個月","createTime":"2021-04-14T02:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T02:14:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"25bee5ca8c8b2b13460c8ea7313e94b3cd102e31","tid":2487931,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:03:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15004&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11JnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=b4202580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15004</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第十四庭 <br />\n#黃士翔裁判官<br />\n#裁決 <br />\n#1118葵涌<br />\n<br />\nD1:冼(18)<br />\nD2:湯(21)<br />\n🛑曾還押54日 <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)D1在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n(2)D2在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n(3)D2無牌管有無線電通訊器具<br />\n<br />\n內庭飛已派晒<br />\n「直播員打錯左十三庭」<br />\n<br />\n【速報】<br />\n‼️罪名不成立‼️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"1fccf6e720823c016ca77fc1dcb9c87a2d3b4d20","tid":2487931,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c1164adbdb65407d682f2a6a5f7599aa5691a0","tid":2487931,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:06:11.000Z","msg":"香港法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未審先坐"},{"pid":"69731db20898d805b70abac4bc450fdf65e72a6c","tid":2487931,"uid":160592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:06:34.000Z","msg":"人生冇左兩個月點計"},{"pid":"d0b13b2f0a0c3b789d99a57431a15cfdbed22fee","tid":2487931,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"更正:兩人均曾還柙近兩個月"},{"pid":"e94bd4627e70d2aa8fe8fca68d718c51a26f1f1d","tid":2487931,"uid":219537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:07:36.000Z","msg":"而家告唔入，有冇得叫律師追番果段時間損失"},{"pid":"3ad24ec3301f8decfeb1f96cf2b9a1406afe41c8","tid":2487931,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:07:59.000Z","msg":"還押時間有錢賠?"},{"pid":"5dea8b07ff5a9fbe6450851ee7597d3ea2798ba4","tid":2487931,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:08:34.000Z","msg":"先前提堂:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9197\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9197&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11JnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=e1f3bd51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9197</a><br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#羅德泉主任裁判官<br />\n#1118葵涌 #提堂<br />\n<br />\nD1冼(17)、D2湯(20)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)、(2)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器 [D1, D2]<br />\n各被控於2019年11月18日，在葵涌葵馥苑附近管有攻擊性武器，即各一瓶高濃度腐蝕性液體，樽外用紗布包裹着一片懷疑漂白錠<br />\n(3)無牌管有無線電通訊器具 [D2]<br />\n<br />\n案情：被指於11月18日在葵涌葵馥苑近43號巴士站管有攻擊性武器，即各一瓶高濃度硫酸，樽外用紗布包裹着一片漂白錠，控方指硫酸與藥片產生的氯氣對人體有害<br />\n<br />\n背景：２人在11月20日首次上庭，被 #羅德泉主任裁判官 拒絕保釋申請；11月28日保釋覆核亦被 #羅德泉主任裁判官 拒絕；湯在12月6日向高等法院原訟庭 #彭寶琴法官 申請保釋被拒；冼在12月16日向高等法院原訟庭 #李素蘭法官 申請保釋被拒；２人還押54天後，終在1月13日獲准以5000元保釋，期間不得離港及須每週報到２次，並須禁足葵馥苑。<br />\n<br />\nD1代表律師正在與律政司方面溝通，申請押後4星期至10月7日答辯。控方沒有反對。<br />\n裁判官問及D2代表律師意見，D2希望與D1一同答辯，故此一同押後4星期<br />\n裁判官批准押後。<br />\n<br />\n辯方無更改保釋條件申請<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至10月7日0930 西九龍法院第一庭進行答辯<br />\n✅期間以原有條款保釋✅<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"589c1faa318c9563a9b301f54d881727e8559d6e","tid":2487931,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:09:21.000Z","msg":"鳩拉鳩告無後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816f100d45168cb8cc83b3eb3c44e7c6d20a223a","tid":2487931,"uid":235814,"like":0,"disl